# Title: Rundll32 InstallScreenSaver Execution
# Author: Christopher Peacock @securepeacock, SCYTHE @scythe_io, TactiKoolSec
# Date: 2022-04-28
# Level: medium
# Description: An attacker may execute an application as a SCR File using rundll32.exe desk.cpl,InstallScreenSaver
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1218.011
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_rundll32_installscreensaver.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate installation of a new screensaver

CommandLine="*InstallScreenSaver*" Image="*\\rundll32.exe" OR OriginalFileName="RUNDLL32.EXE"